message: Hi Bob, I'm offering this item for $130. I think it's a fair price considering its value.
Hello Alice, thank you for your offer. I believe I can come to an agreement of $100 for the product.
Hi Bob, thanks for your offer. I see you're interested! How about we meet in the middle at $115?
Hello Alice, I appreciate your willingness to negotiate. I would like to propose $105 as my offer for the product.
